    <criterion testable="true">`git status` shows zero changes under `src/`, `power-platform/`, `infra/`, `scripts/`</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`CustomWebAppFactory.cs` is NOT modified</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    <execution-result date="2026-05-31" wave="2.4" rigor="FULL">
      OUTCOME: SUCCESS — 63/63 cluster failures cleared with no escalation.

      ROOT-CAUSE INVESTIGATION (per scope-extension hint):
        - Integration.Workspace.WorkspaceEndpointsTests (31, 100% rate): SINGLE root cause —
          `WorkspaceTestFixture` configuration dict missing the 7 keys Wave 1.3 task 018
          added to `CustomWebAppFactory.cs`. AiPersistenceModule threw on
          `CosmosPersistence:Endpoint is not configured` during `CreateHost`.
        - Integration.Workspace.WorkspaceLayoutEndpointTests (23, 100% rate): SAME root
          cause — `WorkspaceLayoutTestFixture` inherits from `WorkspaceTestFixture`.
        - Integration.CommunicationIntegrationTests (9, 33% rate): SEPARATE root cause —
          production refactored `CommunicationService.SendAsync` from
          `_dataverseService.CreateAsync(...)` to `_genericEntityService.CreateAsync(...)`
          (line 780 of CommunicationService.cs). 9 tests mocked `IDataverseService.CreateAsync`;
          assertion-level test-stale.

      FIXES (test-only, NFR-01 + NFR-02 compliant):
        1. WorkspaceTestFixture.cs (+19/-0, 5.6% of 341 lines): added 7 missing config keys
           (CosmosPersistence:Endpoint, CosmosPersistence:DatabaseName, AgentService:Enabled,
           AgentService:Endpoint, AgentService:AgentId, AgentService:MaxConcurrency,
           AgentService:ThreadCacheExpiryMinutes) — mirroring Wave 1.3 task 018's
           CustomWebAppFactory.cs additions. → 52/54 Workspace failures cleared in ONE edit.
        2. WorkspaceEndpointsTests.cs (+1/-0, 0.1%): added `[Trait("status","repaired")]`.
        3. WorkspaceLayoutEndpointTests.cs (+29/-16, 7.6%): added class-level Trait; updated
           2 assertion-level tests for Wave 2b (task 109) contract change:
             - GetLayouts_AuthenticatedRequest_Returns200WithSystemAndUserLayouts: now
               asserts 5 layouts (1 hard-coded + 2 Dataverse-system + 2 user; the
               WithUserLayouts(2) mock returns the same 2 entities to both queries).
             - GetDefaultLayout_NoUserDefault_ReturnsCorporateWorkspaceFallback (renamed
               to ...ReturnsNullBody): production cascade now returns 200 OK with
               null/empty body when no default exists (per Wave 2b production change).
        4. CommunicationIntegrationTests.cs (+56/-36, 4.7%): extended `BuildService` to
           accept optional `Mock<IGenericEntityService>`; updated 7 send-flow tests to
           wire CreateAsync mock onto `IGenericEntityService` (production redirect) instead
           of `IDataverseService` (now no-longer-used for Communication record creation).

      §6.2 TRAITS APPLIED:
        - WorkspaceEndpointsTests → `[Trait("status","repaired")]`
        - WorkspaceLayoutEndpointTests → `[Trait("status","repaired")]`
        - CommunicationIntegrationTests → `[Trait("status","repaired")]` (already present)

      ESCALATIONS (§4.8): NONE — all per-file diffs &lt;10% line replacement;
        largest is WorkspaceLayoutEndpointTests at 7.6%.

      REAL-BUG LEDGER: NO new entries — all 63 failures classified `test-stale`
        (test-fixture config gap + assertion drift after production-refactor).

      VERIFICATION:
        Pre-edit: 63 Failed (31 + 23 + 9) in batch scope; 72 Failed across full Integration namespace.
        Post-edit (targeted): `--filter "FullyQualifiedName~Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests.Integration"` =
          443 Total / 428 Passed / 15 Skipped / **0 Failed**. (Skips include 4 pre-existing
          Communication Skips, 11 from sibling batches/clusters; sibling tasks 061/062 also
          contributed.)
        Build (`dotnet build -c Release`): **0 errors / 17 pre-existing warnings**.
        `git status`: zero changes under `src/`/`power-platform/`/`infra/`/`scripts/`.
        `CustomWebAppFactory.cs`: NOT modified (§4.5 OK).

      QUALITY GATES (Step 9.5):
        - NFR-01 (no production change): ✅
        - NFR-02 (&lt;50% rewrite per file): ✅ (max 7.6%)
        - NFR-03 (no new DI in tests): ✅ (config dict + optional mock parameter only)
        - NFR-09 (repair-not-rewrite): ✅
        - §4.5 (CustomWebAppFactory.cs untouched): ✅
        - §6.2 (final end-state Trait on every touched test class): ✅
        - ADR-001/007/013-refined/028: respected (no AI-coupling or facade changes).
    </execution-result>
